pageTitle: Itinerary for Wednesday, January 11, 2017 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Itinerary for the Prime Minister, Justin Trudeau, for Wednesday, January 11, 2017:

Ottawa, Ontario

9:30 a.m. The Prime Minister will meet with the Native Women’s Association of Canada.

Queen’s Room, Prime Minister’s Office
Centre Block
Parliament Hill
Ottawa, Ontario       

Note for media:

  • Pooled photo opportunity at the beginning of the meeting
